      "inheritance_hierarchy": "Size.sol inherits: SizeView (abstract) -> SizeStorage (holds State), and also Initializable, AccessControlUpgradeable, PausableUpgradeable, UUPSUpgradeable. SizeView exposes read-only views over SizeStorage.state and wraps several library view helpers (RiskLibrary, AccountingLibrary, UpdateConfig). Token contracts: NonTransferrableScaledToken inherits NonTransferrableToken, which inherits OZ Ownable + OZ ERC20. PriceFeed is standalone implementing IPriceFeed. Business logic is predominantly in libraries operating on State storage via 'using X for State'.",
      "external_dependencies": [
        "OpenZeppelin upgradeable: AccessControlUpgradeable, PausableUpgradeable, Initializable, UUPSUpgradeable",
        "OpenZeppelin (non-upgradeable): Ownable, ERC20, SafeERC20, Address, Strings, SafeCast, IERC20Metadata",
        "Solady FixedPointMathLib (mulDiv, min/max)",
        "Aave v3: IPool, IAToken, WadRayMath (liquidity index scaling)",
        "Chainlink: AggregatorV3Interface (used by PriceFeed)",
        "forge-std (scripts/tests): Script, Vm, stdJson (off-chain tooling)"
      ],
      "upgrade_patterns": "UUPS proxy pattern for Size implementation. Deploy uses ERC1967Proxy pointing to Size/SizeMock and calls Size.initialize via abi.encodeCall. Upgrade authorization is gated by AccessControl (DEFAULT_ADMIN_ROLE). No Diamond pattern detected.",
      "access_control_structure": "Role-based access control via OZ AccessControlUpgradeable on Size: DEFAULT_ADMIN_ROLE controls updateConfig and upgrades; PAUSER_ROLE controls pause/unpause; BORROW_RATE_UPDATER_ROLE controls setVariablePoolBorrowRate; KEEPER_ROLE controls liquidateWithReplacement. Note: AccessControl management functions (grantRole/revokeRole/renounceRole) are externally accessible as inherited public/external functions."
    },
